<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="conduct-vt">conduct <strong><em>vt</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /kən'dʌkt/    美 /kən'dʌkt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>引导；带领：</strong></h4>
<p>to lead or guide sb through or around a place：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The guide conducted us around the West Lake. 
导游带领我们游览了西湖。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>指挥 (军队、乐队等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My friend went home, leaving me to conduct the band.
我朋友回家了，留下我指挥乐队。</p><footer>北师大④ – 12</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>实施；管理；进行</strong></h4>
<p>to organize or do a particular activity：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>conduct an experiment / an interview / a survey</strong>
进行实验/面试/调查</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A lot of research is being conducted in this area.
很多研究工作正在这个领域内展开。</p><footer>2010 陕西</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>So far we have conducted a variety of activities on English learning.
目前我们已经开展了各种各样的英语学习活动。</p><footer>2010 湖南书面表达</footer></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>举止；表现：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Make sure you <strong>conduct yourself</strong> as a good neighbor should.
确保你的行为举止是一个好邻居应该有的。</p><footer>2018 浙江</footer></div></div>